history.created_by: RUN |2 TARGETARCH=arm64 DUPLICACY_WEB_VERSION=1.8.1 /bin/sh -c apk --update add --no-cache bash ca-certificates dbus  su-exec tzdata                                       &&      export DUPLICACY_ARCH=$(case $TARGETARCH in "amd64") echo "x64" ;; "arm") echo "arm" ;; "arm64") echo "arm64" ;; *) echo "unsupported_arch";; esac) &&     export DUPLICACY_URL=https://acrosync.com/duplicacy-web/duplicacy_web_linux_${DUPLICACY_ARCH}_${DUPLICACY_WEB_VERSION} &&     echo "Fetching duplicacy binary from ${DUPLICACY_URL}"                                                      &&     wget -nv -O /usr/local/bin/duplicacy_web  ${DUPLICACY_URL} 2>&1                                             &&     chmod +x /usr/local/bin/duplicacy_web                                                                       &&     rm -f /var/lib/dbus/machine-id && ln -s /config/machine-id /var/lib/dbus/machine-id # buildkit
